      <title>公告 | 网站内容征集</title>
      <link href="/blog/solicitation/"/>
      <url>/blog/solicitation/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>是的，这个网站真的真的只是个开头，还有很多不完善的地方<br>所以，如果你有能力<br>你也可以为网站的内容完善出一份力<br>对征集内容有想法的，欢迎发送邮件至<strong>hi@mail.hipeach.cn</strong><br>我十分十分十分愿意听取你的建议</p><hr><h3 id="主页标题动态字幕显示"><a href="#主页标题动态字幕显示" class="headerlink" title="主页标题动态字幕显示"></a><strong>主页标题动态字幕显示</strong></h3><p>主页中一直在变化的动态字幕<br>你可以<a href="https://hipeach.cn" title="返回主页">返回主页</a>查看字幕效果<br>内容要求<strong>与哈利•波特及其衍生内容有关</strong><br><strong>最好提供内容出处，需要提供英文版，禁止机翻</strong><br>下方为已有的字幕内容<br><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- 过人的聪明才智是人类最大的财富。</span><br><span class="line">- Wit beyond measure is man&#x27;s greatest treasure.</span><br><span class="line">- 一个人的出身并不重要，重要的是他成长为什么样的人！</span><br><span class="line">- It matters not what someone is born, But what they grow to be!</span><br><span class="line">- 对于头脑十分清醒的人来说，死亡不过是另一场伟大的冒险。</span><br><span class="line">- To the well-organized mind, Death is but the next great adventure.</span><br><span class="line">- 沉溺于虚幻的梦想，而忘记现实的生活，这是毫无益处的，千万记住。</span><br><span class="line">- It does not do to dwell on dreams and forget to live, Remember that.</span><br><span class="line">- 暂时使痛苦变得麻木，只会使你最后感觉疼痛时疼得更加厉害。</span><br><span class="line">- Numbing the pain for a while will make it worse when you fanally feel it.</span><br><span class="line">- 表现我们真正自我的是我们的选择，选择比我们的能力重要得多。</span><br><span class="line">- It is our choices that show what we truly are, Far more than our abilities.</span><br><span class="line">- 人们容易原谅别人的错误，却很难原谅别人的正确。</span><br><span class="line">- People find it far easier to forgive others for being wrong than being right.</span><br><span class="line">- 当我们面对死亡和黑暗时，我们害怕的只是未知，除此之外没有别的。</span><br><span class="line">- It is the unknown we fear when we look upon death and darkness, Nothing more.</span><br><span class="line">- 对事物永远使用正确的称呼。对一个名字的恐惧，会强化对这个事物本身的恐惧。</span><br><span class="line">- Always use the proper name for things.Fear of a name increases fear of the thing itself.</span><br><span class="line">- 真相，这是一种美丽而可怕的东西，需要格外谨慎地对待。</span><br><span class="line">- The truth, It is a beautiful and terrible thing, And should therefore be treated with great caution.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="Aplayer音乐播放器"><a href="#Aplayer音乐播放器" class="headerlink" title="Aplayer音乐播放器"></a><strong>Aplayer音乐播放器</strong></h3><p>主页左下角的音乐播放器<br>你可以<strong>分享你的歌</strong>单，让网站增添亿点点新鲜血液<br>你仍然可以<a href="https://hipeach.cn" title="返回主页">返回主页</a>查看效果<br>下方为需要的数据内容及获取方法<br><strong>请仔细阅读，否则你发送的内容可能不被采纳！</strong><br><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">音乐平台：[网易云音乐]netease  [QQ音乐]tencent  [酷狗音乐]kugou  [虾米音乐]xiami  [千千音乐]baidu</span><br><span class="line">数据类型：[歌曲]song  [歌单]playlist  [专辑]album  [搜索]search  [歌手]artist</span><br><span class="line">内容代码：歌曲ID/歌单ID/专辑ID/搜索关键字</span><br><span class="line">-----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">如何获取数据类型与内容代码？</span><br><span class="line">在网页打开一首歌或专辑或歌单</span><br><span class="line">查看它的网址</span><br><span class="line">例如网址为  [https:<span class="comment">//music.163.com/#/song?id=1417055605]</span></span><br><span class="line">Song就是数据类型，<span class="number">1417055605</span>就是内容代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="404页面图片"><a href="#404页面图片" class="headerlink" title="404页面图片"></a><strong>404页面图片</strong></h3><p>404页面<em>[网页不存在时显示的页面]</em>显示的图片<br>你可以去<a href="https://hipeach.cn/404" title="404页面">404页面</a>查看效果<br><strong><em>图片需要符合法律规定，严禁涉黄！！！</em></strong><br>下方为目前的404图片<br><a href="https://hipeach.cn/media/page404.jpg" title="Page404"><img src="/media/page404.jpg" alt="Page404" title="Page404"></a></p><h3 id="网站未来发展方向"><a href="#网站未来发展方向" class="headerlink" title="网站未来发展方向"></a><strong>网站未来发展方向</strong></h3><p>没错，你没看错，就是<strong>网站未来的发展方向</strong><br>在这个项目中，你可以畅所欲言<br>写出你想写的任何东西<br>你的言论可能决定了网站将来何去何从<br>既然这么重要，为何留到最后呢？<br>因为不是每个人都有提出这种建议的能力<br>而且我也想在这个地方倾注更多我的心血<br>但，如果你有更好的想法<br>欢迎你提出来，我也许会采纳你的意见</p><hr><p><strong>以上就是目前需要收集的所有内容，感谢你看到这里<br>如果你有好的建议、想法<br>请发送邮件到hi@mail.hipeach.icu<br>如果你想要分享我需要内容，请务必在邮件中提及分享内容的标题<br>这十分重要，务必记住</strong></p><p><strong><em>更新在2022.03.30</em></strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
